title: Wednesday Post Show (10-12-22)
itunes:title: Wednesday Post Show (10-12-22)
description:
We talked about Actress Angela Lansbury from Murder She Wrote dying at 96. Also that "American Idol" runner-up Willie Spence dying in a car crash. A woman who gave birth 48 hours after finding out she was pregnant. Would you rather have time to prepare and stress or not know a baby was coming?  We get into a discussion about hiring police escorts. Bobby talks about his ideal dinner time.
